    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in mint condition. The exterior is clean with no visible dents, scratches, or paint issues. The interior shows no wear \u2014 upholstery and all surfaces are in like-new condition. Mechanically, the car runs well with no known issues. All systems and components are functioning properly.",
      "price": 46500.0,
